name: Issue 4
description:

name: The Find T-Shirt + Extras (Blue Version)
description:
To celebrate our second anniversary, we bring you this limited edition 'The Find Mag Goodie Bag'. For only 25 EU (34 USD) you are in for a special treat: 

+ A limited edition The Find Mag t-shirt, made in collaboration with Project Mooncircle
+ Three exclusive digital tracks off our 'The Find Rewind' tape
+ The first ten orders receive one of the very last physical copies of our beat tape 'The Find Rewind'.
+ A discount code for our future projects
+ FREE shipping in Europe!

Shirt details: 
White silkscreen print on 100% cotton, B&C Exact 190 (Cyan Blue) model. Designed by The Binh (Project Mooncircle) and printed by More Color (Freshcotton, Vage Gasten, Pete Philly & Perquisite a.o.). 

Front detail: http://bit.ly/9e8bWy   Back detail: http://bit.ly/dgyehy

name: Tape: The Find Rewind
description:
'The Find Rewind' is a limited edition tape featuring unreleased instrumental tracks by a wide array of producers. Hip Hop is the main ingredient, but influences from genres as Jazz, Soul and Electronic music are evident. 

Line up: 
Incise, Suff Daddy, Arts The Beatdoctor, St/Mic, K-Murdock (of Panacea), Pat D, Stro The 89th Key (formerly of The Procussions), Kev Brown, Factor, Weedy (of 40 Winks), Daru Jones, Kero One, Jazz Chronicles, LuiGi, Free The Robots, Full Crate, Destruments, Mr. Modo, Headnodic (of Crown City Rockers, Bun, Mr. Viane (of Mr. Popcorn), Dela, Block Barley & Matthew David

More info:
